						<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
							Aplicaciones nativas y multiplataforma para iOS y Android con experiencias de usuario excepcionales.
						</p>
						<ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-1">
							<li>• React Native & Flutter</li>
							<li>• Apps nativas iOS/Android</li>
							<li>• Integración con APIs</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<!-- Backend Development -->
					<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-green-100 p-8 rounded-xl hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
							<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 12h14M5 12a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2M5 12a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2m-2-4h.01M17 16h.01"></path>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Backend & APIs</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
							Arquitecturas robustas y escalables con Node.js, Python, y bases de datos modernas.
						</p>
						<ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-1">
							<li>• APIs RESTful y GraphQL</li>
							<li>• Microservicios</li>
							<li>• Cloud & DevOps</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<!-- AI Customer Service -->
					<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-50 to-blue-100 p-8 rounded-xl hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500 to-blue-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
							<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"></path>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">IA Customer Service</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
							Chatbots inteligentes con IA para WhatsApp, Telegram y Facebook que revolucionan la atención al cliente.
						</p>
						<ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-1">
							<li>• Chatbots con OpenAI GPT</li>
							<li>• Integración multi-plataforma</li>
